---
title: Steak Fajitas on the Grill with Lime Crema and Southwestern Spices
description: Ready, set, grill! We couldn’t think of a better way to kick off a Fourth of July cookout than with some juicy steaks sizzled on the grates. Although the meat isn’t the only thing in these fajitas that’s got a nice char: the tortillas, bell pepper, and onion are grilled too. And while that smoky flavor from the flames may be the epitome of summertime eating, no need to fret if you can’t fire up a grill—this dish also can be made indoors.
